# Pipeline Repository Agents Guide

## Commit Message Format

- Subject: `<TICKET>: add package <package_name> into 'onboarding' collection`
- Body: include the summary and any builder MR dependency notes
- Trailer: `Closes: <TICKET>`

## Collection Structure

Packages are added to `collections/onboarding/<variant>/requirements/<package>.txt`.
Each file contains a single line with the package specifier and tracking comment.
